description: Visually inspect the battery compartment inside the power supply module for proper battery installation (correct orientation and good contact with terminals), and check for signs of corrosion or broken wires around the battery holder., outcome='The visual inspection of the battery and battery internal resistor showed no observable internal faults. No issues such as corrosion or broken wires were noted. Battery orientation and terminal contact were not reported as problematic.\nCurrent persistent circuit state [differences with the starting state]:\nNo circuit-level changes introduced by diagnostics.', precise_action_cost=30.0, cost_breakdown=[('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0)], simplified_outcome=None), DiagnosticActionResult(action=
name: Observe -> Control module internal wiring (series connections),
description: Visually inspect the internal wiring inside the control modules, especially where the series path continues through each module, to check for any breaks, disconnected wires, or obvious internal faults that might interrupt continuity through the modules despite external cable connections being intact., outcome='All eight control switches were visually inspected and found to be closed with no observable internal faults. No breaks, disconnected wires, or obvious internal faults were detected inside any of the control module enclosures.\nCurrent persistent circuit state [differences with the starting state]:\nNo circuit-level changes introduced by diagnostics.', precise_action_cost=160.0, cost_breakdown=[('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0)], simplified_outcome=None), DiagnosticActionResult(action=
name: Observe -> Load module internal wiring (diode and lamp circuit),
description: Open the load module enclosure and visually inspect the internal wiring, diode, and lamp connections for any visible breaks, burnt components, or signs of disconnection that could interrupt the current path to the lamp., outcome='The internal inspection found no visible breaks, burns, or disconnections in the diode, main load lamp, internal indicator lamp, or load input cables. Both lamps are not lit, but none of the inspected components show observable internal faults. There is no indication of polarity inversion based on the cable observations provided.\nCurrent persistent circuit state [differences with the starting state]:\nNo circuit-level changes introduced by diagnostics.', precise_action_cost=60.0, cost_breakdown=[('open_inspection_panel', 5.0), ('open_peephole', 5.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0)], simplified_outcome=None)] 
